[Student "S"]
{This is a companion hand to Deal 13.

EAST has 14 points, the same strength she had in Deal 13. But what a difference. 
This time WEST's \S shortness complements her hand very well. She bids 4\C 
to show her Control, and after WEST shows the \DA she 
uses Blackwood to make sure WEST also has the trump Ace.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "S"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
