[Student "S"]
{WEST bids 3\S to show a strong hand with a singleton \S. 

After EAST shows her first-round \C control WEST decides he will bid slam if EAST has three Aces.

When Blackwood reveals just two Aces in EAST, WEST stops at 5\H.}

